{"tid":1138974,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"震撼奇景！NASA公開火星日出日落照","createTime":"2019-05-05T01:47:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-05T05:08:42.000Z","uid":32511,"like":21,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"19744913daed56501a4d0dbae4b18b84ac8c78bc","tid":1138974,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T01:47:35.000Z","msg":"人們追逐懸日美景，科學家醉心於火星的日出日落！無人探測器洞察號（InSight）於2018年11月27日降落火星以來，陸續傳回地球照片。美國國家太空總署（NASA）最新公布「洞察號」抓拍到的一組最新照片，呈現出火星上日出和日落的景象。由於火星與太陽的距離遠大於地球與太陽的距離，這組照片曝光引起震撼。<br />\n <br />\n俄羅斯《消息報》報導，NASA下屬的噴射推進實驗室（JPL）1日在其官網上發布了這組照片。照片攝於4月24日和25日，也是「洞察號」登陸火星後的第145個火星日，由「洞察號」機械臂上的相機拍攝。機械臂上的相機於火星時間早晨5時30分和傍晚6時30分左右分別拍攝了日出和日落的場景。「洞察號」甲板下的相機還拍到了一些漂浮在火星天空中的雲層。<br />\n <br />\n由於火星與太陽的距離遠大於地球與太陽的距離，因此火星上看到的太陽大小只有地球上看到的約三分之二。NASA在官網上提供了RAW和色彩校正版本的火星日落圖像。色彩校正版本顯示了如果一個人站在火星表面目睹日落時，人眼會看到什麼樣的景象。<br />\n <br />\n洞察號是首個專門揭開火星地質奧秘的探測器，在它24 個月（約一個火星年）值勤期間，科學家預計將探測到10至100 次的火星地震，且洞察號收集的數據將有助他們了解火星大小、密度及組成。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nqsAOb7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnqsAOb7.png&h=de39f92e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/93KvB5t.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F93KvB5t.png&h=1685c0f7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cij7EiO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fcij7EiO.png&h=ea23372e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9CnJcDP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9CnJcDP.png&h=34e81a94&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5e700be6a2e9d1461dec1327bc12fa449c65701a","tid":1138974,"uid":64071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T01:50:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e99505b0cf25accb7f05a579f60c3bc44472305","tid":1138974,"uid":200280,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T02:11:38.000Z","msg":"好孤獨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ae26d436dce0ea43cbe8a91baab667077cc3cb6","tid":1138974,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T02:25:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6dcc9f755ac22bdc1bb56cb7dcab751c40c29f7a","tid":1138974,"uid":175523,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T03:38:19.000Z","msg":"好滄桑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccbad4808d1156ae4128e4dfe10fa01dd2797a9b","tid":1138974,"uid":39012,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T03:42:55.000Z","msg":"原來火星地面唔係紅色<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5fc2a20acee8d57798bcefc95ec5ad93ba16bb3","tid":1138974,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T03:47:01.000Z","msg":"話時話，插左美國🇺🇸，算唔算美國領土如果開始殖民嘅話<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61a6f5a1ab0892e9b2887c3b83272887d04672f7","tid":1138974,"uid":213996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T03:56:26.000Z","msg":"原來火星同山地差唔多"},{"pid":"f5d24883d5c6ce2f0822062db569e92d683d5282","tid":1138974,"uid":103513,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T04:06:46.000Z","msg":"細到粒豆咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97043a66f0fb861330b5fc4ebd38a420421974ef","tid":1138974,"uid":49004,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T04:12:14.000Z","msg":"你那太空艙 能夠發出金色的光<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c82b6b4422c157c8efe5d30e8ed2c2e314fcacf4","tid":1138974,"uid":196735,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T04:15:54.